summary: AC DRAIN HAS STOPPED UP 4 TIMES OVER THE LIFETIME OF THE CAR RESULTING IN LOTS OF WATER TO OVERFLOW ON THE CARPET OF THE CAR CAUSING DAMAGE TO THE CARPET. ACCORDING TO THE SERVICE DEALER, "THE DRAIN MAY CLOG UP AT ANY TIME."  WHAT IS THE PROBLEM WITH THIS DRAIN?  I'VE NEVER HAD A CAR DO THAT BEFORE.  *JB
